{"tid":689234,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"狗巴特約K-1 巴膠格鬥會-沙田馬場站","createTime":"2018-06-04T02:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T04:32:59.000Z","uid":72280,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"854af8ca2991c9ee14b435d2bd0f43d9cdb51a5e","tid":689234,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"歡迎收睇今日係沙田馬場舉行<br />\n狗巴特約K-1 巴膠格鬥會<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/010049_a3bbd0a19fb0b42552b6107f5b9d9dba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F010049_a3bbd0a19fb0b42552b6107f5b9d9dba.png&h=0830b4ce&s={SIZE}\" />[<br />\n<br />\n今日兩位巴膠會示範周星星係打電話問功夫常用的招式<br />\n首先黎個納爾遜式鎖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/224859_37715c86c3b7c04615b98ca7cc204161.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F224859_37715c86c3b7c04615b98ca7cc204161.png&h=4e6a242e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再黎個奪命鉸剪腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/225639_6141f65f9ba9ff920d512229667c6935.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F225639_6141f65f9ba9ff920d512229667c6935.png&h=cb3f95d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/225415_5b71a8cd49d607ff0fe0e79b5065212e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F225415_5b71a8cd49d607ff0fe0e79b5065212e.png&h=3adf3fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/225440_9c9dcb3e523029585ec49aa6643d918e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F225440_9c9dcb3e523029585ec49aa6643d918e.png&h=f37d5cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/225541_da56